## ğŸ’¡ What Makes It Different?

* Works entirely on WhatsApp.
* Responds automatically â€” no human needed.
* Can handle images (e.g., "find similar shirts to this picture").
* Learns user preferences over time.
* Supports multiple languages, including Nigerian Pidgin.

