## ğŸ¤– How the Bot Behaves

The bot has a simple, friendly personality:

* Polite
* Fast to respond
* Gives the user clear options
* Never overwhelms them with too many choices

It can:

* Ask clarifying questions
* Provide options based on user requests
* Send followâ€‘up suggestions (e.g., new arrivals, price alerts)
* Understand natural language ("I need something for a wedding on Saturday")

